    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《苦痛殿堂》是一款生存游戏，画面采用预先渲染的复古风，类似于1990年代晚期的角色扮演游戏。从多名英雄角色中选择一名操控，并进入致命的苦痛殿堂闯荡。对抗不洁的恐怖生物，并在敌人一波波的攻势下努力求生，直到其中一位苦痛领主登场。使用角色特长、技能和物品强化英雄。在闯关过程中打造全新强力流派。探索地底的各个地方，寻找全新的强力物品，让你能够闯入更黑暗的深渊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/4d11909190f0b16281070c3e5a0711c7.poster.avif?t=1761660851\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/4d11909190f0b16281070c3e5a0711c7.webm?t=1761660851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/4d11909190f0b16281070c3e5a0711c7.mp4?t=1761660851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >闯关只要30分钟，轻松又快速</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典预先渲染美术风格</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务导向的游戏进程</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种不同的技能、特长和物品可供选择，让你搭配出有趣的组合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种不同的头目，主打独特机制和攻击模式</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多名各具特色的角色，让你能够体验多种玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁并探索多个有趣且高难度的地底世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可送回游戏主世界并用于后续闯关的独特物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调制魔法药水，让命运女神祝你一臂之力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁各个职业的力量，并和你指定的角色结合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败地底世界的领主并探索永无止境的培养系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到稀有版本的物品，进一步优化你的流派配置</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏后期测试你策略的强度，挑战难以攻克的苦痛神庙</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/d4e7ed9d9d2780f85ea2b5f7b7d30b7b.poster.avif?t=1761660851\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/d4e7ed9d9d2780f85ea2b5f7b7d30b7b.webm?t=1761660851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/d4e7ed9d9d2780f85ea2b5f7b7d30b7b.mp4?t=1761660851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完整内容清单</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6个关卡，环境各具特色</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >11名可扮演角色和角色印记</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >25个祝福，能在闯关过程中使你强大</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60种不同的物品可供收集和解锁</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >240个稀有度更高版本的物品</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >74个技能和技能升级</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30个神器，可用来调整游戏体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过35个独特首领</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过70种独特怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过500个任务可完成</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过1000个特长，可用来升级角色和技能</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/f0c9400d9fab239e9c04135b05627220.poster.avif?t=1761660851\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/f0c9400d9fab239e9c04135b05627220.webm?t=1761660851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218750/extras/f0c9400d9fab239e9c04135b05627220.mp4?t=1761660851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
